snippet.title: Section One
snippet.description:
Section 1 - T.V. Show Hosted by Attorneys at Law Stefan Ramkissoon and Kiel Taklalsingh live Radio and T.V. Jaagriti every Sunday afternoon.
Section 1 of our constitution declares our nation to be sovereign democratic state. This declaration only has meaning when citizens of this country resolve themselves to defend our democracy. Section 1 seeks to raise awareness of issues which may threaten our democracy and to become a vehicle for the preservation, promotion and protection our democracy
